headline: US-Canada trade war is a 'major disruption' to auto industry
summary: Canada announces 25% retaliatory tariffs after US President Donald Trump's 25% tariffs on all steel and aluminum imports went into effect overnight. AutoGuide editorial director Greg Migliore joins Wealth with Brad Smith to discuss how tariffs are a "major disruption" to the auto industry.
